ount": 89}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价特斯拉官方回应河南车主「高速刹车失灵」：系右前轮速传感器警报？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "5 月 28 日，特斯拉回应河南温先生近日在网络上声称的车辆「高速刹车失灵」、「险出事故」事件，称目前初步远程诊断车辆报警原因为右前轮速传感器警报，并非「刹车失灵」。 特斯拉还表示，温先生的车辆行驶里程已逾 17.5 万公里，已超出车辆质保期，车辆从出现报警提示至今，已经继续行驶了 800 多公里，并且还在使用中。温先生在拒绝检查车辆的情况下，在网络上声称车辆「高速刹车失灵」、「险出事故」，并使用「自杀玩具」等词汇制造社会热点，向特斯拉提出免费更换至新款 Model X 车型的诉求，对此特斯拉无法予以满足。（新浪财经）"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-5f499fa156f7d621511f8d6d33e13d75_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "267 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/461826911"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IjP3H0O+f66U1EAMaCDY0OTA3NTgyIPXHwYUGMA84/wFAFnIJNDYxODI2OTExeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "23_1622190832.1062064", "card_id": "Q_461764476", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 82}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待 Epic 平台 5 月 27 日免费送出狼人杀游戏《Among Us》？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-9b8c069143e5c5003a1652e73a4e960e_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "260 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/461764476"}, "text_tag_area": {"text": "Epic 亲自答", "font_color": "GYL01A", "background": "GYL01A"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IjP3H0O+f66U1EAMaCDY0ODkzNzYwIJ3qvoUGMAM4ogFAF3IJNDYxNzY0NDc2eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "24_1622190832.1067612", "card_id": "Q_438113905", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 444}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "备孕和不备孕区别大吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-b82be8bc8765a8b6f25db86a79b16bfc_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "223 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https